### 1. Health Check
GET http://localhost:3000/api

### 2. Share Text (1 Hour Expiry)
POST http://localhost:3000/api/share
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "type": "text",
  "content": "This is a secret message.",
  "duration": "1h",
  "burnOnRead": false
}

### 3. Share Link (Burn on Read)
POST http://localhost:3000/api/share
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "type": "link",
  "content": "https://github.com",
  "duration": "1d",
  "burnOnRead": true
}

